<br>
Personaly, if I am in a pickup group, I think that all good loot (spells included) should be an all who have not won yet roll. <br>
<br>
If I am in a guild group, I don't because I would just give the spell to guildies anyhow. </FONT><br><br><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><B>Results (total votes = 635):</B></FONT><table bgcolor=#FFFFFF border=0 cellpadding=3 cellspacing=0 width="75%"><tbody><tr><td bgcolor="#000000" colspan=3 height=1></tr><TR BGCOLOR=#000000><TD NOWRAP><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Yes, Pure Melee's should get to roll no matter what, Mama needs a new set of armor!</FONT>&nbsp</td><td height><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>142&nbsp;/&nbsp;22.4%</FONT>&nbsp</td><td><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/bar.gif width=67 height=10 hspace=3>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#000000" colspan=3 height=1></tr><TR BGCOLOR=#000000><TD NOWRAP><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Maybe, Melee's should get to roll in a pick up group but should defer to friend/guildy casters.</FONT>&nbsp</td><td height><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>317&nbsp;/&nbsp;49.9%</FONT>&nbsp</td><td><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/bar.gif width=149 height=10 hspace=3>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#000000" colspan=3 height=1></tr><TR BGCOLOR=#000000><TD NOWRAP><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>No, Melee's should never roll on parchments if there is a caster!</FONT>&nbsp</td><td height><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>176&nbsp;/&nbsp;27.7%</FONT>&nbsp</td><td><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/bar.gif width=83 height=10 hspace=3>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#000000" colspan=3 height=1></tr></tbody></table><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showMessage?topicID=1603.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Vote Now</FONT></a> &nbsp <p>Aveen Lucenthawk<br>
