eedy as hell.  That means they roll on everything.  However in rare occations you will find people who belive in NBG (Need before Greed) so it really depends on the group.  In my experiance it is best to discuss this before you began adventuring so that people agree and are informed.  Most loot disputes occure when people do not clearly communicate.<br>
